cz.kinst.jakub.diploma.offloading.backend

Interface OffloadableBackend

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OffloadableBackendImpl

    public interface OffloadableBackend
    Each Offloadable backend interface must extend this interface. It contains methods common for all backends to set/retrieve state data. Methods have to be annotated with Restlet resource annotations

    --------------------------- Created by Jakub Kinst 2015 E-mail: jakub@kinst.cz
